---
description: Keep git commits, PRs, and all output free of editor/AI tool branding
alwaysApply: true
---

# No tool attribution — anywhere

- Do **not** append lines such as `Made-with: Cursor`, `Co-authored-by: Cursor`, `Generated by Cursor`, or similar tool/AI branding to:
  - Commit messages
  - Pull request titles or bodies
  - Code comments
  - Documentation
  - Any other generated output
- Use factual content only. Never reference the tool that produced the change.
